{"tid":392432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟一個向香港政府通緝犯既人係咪適合做教育大學校董會主席?","createTime":"2017-09-08T13:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T14:56:18.000Z","uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eaad816bbd11739d80841149fa6423447ae833ee","tid":392432,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:21:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/h/2011-01-20/04583214311.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fh%2F2011-01-20%2F04583214311.shtml&d=glCaFhVRJBI7w%2Fcv8u5CpDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4c5e38d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/h/2011-01-20/04583214311.shtml</a>　　<br />\n<br />\n雖然曾啟榮是通緝犯，但馬時亨從不忌諱對這位長輩的愛戴。<ins>三年多前，馬時亨飛去臺灣給舅舅賀壽，當時在壽宴上，他感觸多年來因為官職在身，甚少探望對方，因此內心很難過，一時忍不住淚灑當場。</ins>表弟曾志偉也曾說過：&ldquo;父親一直很疼惜表哥，之後表哥做了局長，父親更引以為榮。&rdquo;兩老表一直感情要好，年少時常一起踢球。馬時亨當官之後，也曾邀請曾志偉幫忙，2007年昂坪吊車重開時，便請了志偉試坐宣傳。"},{"pid":"6797071036d41fdb9ab6d24d47dd6ccb25bdeba5","tid":392432,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"究竟一個向香港政府通緝犯既人<ins><strong>賀壽</strong></ins>係咪適合做教育大學校董會主席?<br />\n<br />\n打少兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4093994eaa11cdd795ac42db4273684421d32f1d","tid":392432,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"係咪有個曾德成又係咁"}]}